column1: im just gettin' started!
Played Shaman for the first time, got told to go kill myself 11/10

Transformice is an MMO platformer about dozens of cute mice running to bring back the cheese! Will the almighty Shaman help you or just ruin everything? Millions of levels, hectic physics, skill trees, cosmetics, co-op. It worked, played ok, looked ok, for a Browser game. Gameplay depends on pugging. You need to like Platforming games. Try it, you might like it.
This game is really good!

A great community half full of salt shaking kiddos, a quarter of friendly people and the other quarter keyboard warriors. -1

Once got an entire survivor room (quarter of 24 mice) to call me a cheater and report me for using walls (yes. Walls. In a 2d game.) -1

1000hrs experience of mostly survivor only to be called a "♥♥♥♥♥ noob" for killing the whole room -1

Lagging in survivor benefits you as you get to summon so many cannons at once, so just abuse it and play on (extra info)

Cheaters are so rare, and there isn't any real ranking system (some made ranked survivor and racing) so no worries playing against one +1

Great gamemodes, great game for low end laptops. You can play this game on almost any computer
